         <abstract>
            <p>This article discusses the development and production of the interactive video refresher training program "TOPIC" (Training for Oral Proficiency Interviewing Competence). The oral proficiency interview is a face-to-face test of a candidate's speaking proficiency. TOPIC teaches interviewing and evaluation skills to oral proficiency testers. Under computer control, this interactive video program provides the user with videotaped sample interviews in German, simulation-type activities, and explanations for remedial purposes. The program can be used as a prototype for the development of refresher training programs in other languages. Authoring was done in CDS/Genesis. TOPIC runs on the Sony View System.</p>
         </abstract>
